  "title": "Driver (Class 4) #SGUnitedJobs",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Provide timely delivery to all customers,</li><li>Check and ensure loaded goods are of the correct types according to DO or invoice,</li><li>Ensure goods are delivered in good condition without delay or damage,</li><li>Assist in loading and unloading of goods, able to handle heavy loads,</li><li>Adhere to the statutory and company’s safety policies, procedures and regulations,</li><li>Assisting in adhoc jobs assigned (mainly warehousing/packaging) when not scheduled to do deliveries or any other duties assigned from time to time,</li><li>Coordinate with supervisor and customers for delivery schedule,</li><li>Responsible for the cleanliness and working condition of company's vehicle.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Primary/Secondary School/’N’ level with minimum of 2 years of experience in related field;</li><li>Must possess valid class 4 driving license;</li><li>Clean driving records;</li><li>Familiar with Singapore roads;</li><li>Punctual and hardworking;</li><li>Willing to work 5.5-day work week + OT as required (with good OT pay);</li><li>Working hour: Mon – Fri: 08.30 am to 05.30 pm, Sat: 08.30am to 12.30pm.</li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidate, you may call Elynn at 6542 8733 for fast interview arrangement. Only SG, no quota for work passes.</strong></p>",
