    "description": "<p>AGX Logistics (S) Pte Ltd is incorporated in the year 2010, AGX (Asian Global Xpress) Logistics is an international logistics service provider. As a service-oriented organisation with collective experience of more than 100 years, we are firmly committed towards providing quality and excellent service to all clients. Our focus has always been to deliver cost-effective and efficient solutions to clients. Internal to our client orientated outlook, we offer a wide range of services including Freight Forwarding, Customs Brokerage, Land Transportation, Warehousing, Local Distribution, Door to Door, Exhibition Logistics, Project Cargo, Dangerous Cargo, Valuable Cargo, AOG, VOR, Perishable Cargo, Marine Insurance, Chartering, Packing and Removals at any worldwide destinations.</p>",
